item.description:
This month we're going to focus on communicating with others and incorporating items that we've created with our Adobe applications.  Penny will be presenting you with an Introduction to Constant Contact.  We've had to push our meeting which was scheduled for 3/21 to 3/28 due to a conflict with her schedule, but hopefully this doesn't impact your schedule too much and you can still attend!!  The meeting will be held in Room 256.

We hope to see you next Thursday, 3/28 @ 6:00pm!!

Renae
item.name: March's Manchester Adobe User Group Meeting
